text: Toby Olubi (born 24 September 1987) is a British bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. Prior to appearing at the Olympics, he won £12,000 on Deal or No Deal. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:British male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Great Britain Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
